_Warning: As this doesn't appear to be a bug with Tensorflow, the devs may ask for this to be moved to Stack Overflow._
Please note that from the [Installation Page for Windows](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_windows), Tensorflow is **NOT** supported on Python 2.7 but only **3.5** (or **3.6** in the latest release). Please try again on a newer version of Python.
